      "text": "Yeah, I got scarily good at regex over the years.\n\nAnd, still, I'm using New-Regex -LookAhead/LookBehind every time to make sure I remember the syntax.\n\nNowadays it's pretty common to construct regexes with -join.  I.e.\n\n$spacesOrSymbols = '\\s+', '\\p{S}+' -join '|'"
